1	surgical-face	1	Face	The face,	refined.	Quiet work for the most considered part of the body.	Rhinoplasty, facelift, eyelid surgery, and the subtler refinements — performed in our ACHSI-accredited theatres with a structure-preserving, conservative approach.	\N	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "We approach facial surgery as long-term investment in your face, not a single intervention. A well-judged rhinoplasty looks better at year five than year one. A deep-plane facelift outlasts a SMAS by a decade. We prefer the operation that earns its keep over time — and we will tell you when surgery is the wrong answer.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": "ltr"}}	1	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	0	2026-05-20 12:55:41.793+00	2026-05-20 12:54:44.353+00
